#<AdxTL>@(#)3.0.0.0 $Revision:   1.20  $ Gestión de la máscara SRE2
$ACTION
Case ACTION
 When Default
Endcase
Return

########################################
Subprog S_ZRECOVITM(VALEUR)
Variable Char    VALEUR()

Local File SORDERP [SOP]
Choose [SOP]
& Where [SOP]SOHNUM = [M:SRE2]SRECOVNUM
& Order By [SOP]SOPLIN Asc Using
& [SOP]SOPLIN Titled "Nş Línea",
& [SOP]ITMREF Titled "Artículo"
& Sized(80,240)
& Titled "Selección Artículos Pedido"

If status <> 7
  VALEUR = [SOP]ITMREF
  [M:SRE2]ZSOPLIN = [SOP]SOPLIN
  Affzo [M:SRE2]ZSOPLIN   
Else 
  Raz VALEUR
Endif

Close File [SOP]

End

